<style>
  .kc-ps {
    background: var(--kc-white, #FFFFFF);
    padding: 80px var(--content-padding, 24px);
  }

  .kc-ps__container {
    max-width: var(--max-width, 1200px);
    margin: 0 auto;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 80px;
  }

  .kc-ps__block {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 60px;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .kc-ps__block--reverse .kc-ps__image {
    order: 2;
  }

  .kc-ps__block--reverse .kc-ps__text {
    order: 1;
  }

  .kc-ps__image {
    border-radius: 12px;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .kc-ps__image img {
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
    display: block;
  }

  .kc-ps__image-placeholder {
    width: 100%;
    aspect-ratio: 4 / 3;
    background: var(--kc-alt, #F5F5FA);
    border-radius: 12px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    color: var(--kc-text-secondary, #666666);
    font-size: 15px;
    border: 2px dashed var(--kc-border, #E5E5E5);
  }

  .kc-ps__text {}

  .kc-ps__heading {
    font-family: var(--font-heading, 'DM Serif Display', serif);
    font-size: 32px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--kc-text, #1A1A1A);
    line-height: 1.2;
    margin: 0 0 20px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .kc-ps__body {
    font-family: var(--font-body, 'Inter', sans-serif);
    font-size: 16px;
    color: var(--kc-text-secondary, #666666);
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .kc-ps__body p {
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .kc-ps__body p:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .kc-ps__body strong {
    color: var(--kc-text, #1A1A1A);
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .kc-ps {
      padding: 48px var(--content-padding, 24px);
    }

    .kc-ps__container {
      gap: 48px;
    }

    .kc-ps__block {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 24px;
    }

    .kc-ps__block--reverse .kc-ps__image {
      order: -1;
    }

    .kc-ps__block--reverse .kc-ps__text {
      order: 0;
    }

    .kc-ps__heading {
      font-size: 24px;
    }
  }
</style>

<section class="kc-ps" id="problem-solution">
  <div class="kc-ps__container">
    {%- for block in section.blocks -%}
      <div class="kc-ps__block{% if forloop.index == 2 or forloop.index == 4 %} kc-ps__block--reverse{% endif %}" {{ block.shopify_attributes }}>
        <div class="kc-ps__image">
          {%- if block.settings.image != blank -%}
            {{ block.settings.image | image_url: width: 800 | image_tag: loading: 'lazy', widths: '400,600,800', sizes: '(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 50vw' }}
          {%- else -%}
            <div class="kc-ps__image-placeholder">Section image</div>
          {%- endif -%}
        </div>
        <div class="kc-ps__text">
          <h2 class="kc-ps__heading">{{ block.settings.heading }}</h2>
          <div class="kc-ps__body">{{ block.settings.text }}</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    {%- endfor -%}
  </div>
</section>

{% schema %}
{
  "name": "KC Problem / Solution",
  "tag": "section",
  "class": "kc-ps-section",
  "settings": [],
  "blocks": [
    {
      "type": "block",
      "name": "Content Block",
      "settings": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "id": "heading",
          "label": "Heading",
          "default": "Your Nails Aren't Damaged — They're Infected"
        },
        {
          "type": "richtext",
          "id": "text",
          "label": "Body Text",
          "default": "<p>Years of exposure to moisture, public spaces, and tight shoes didn't weaken your nails — they <strong>infected</strong> them with fungus that burrowed deep under the surface.</p><p>That yellowing? That thickness? That crumbling? It's not aging. It's not genetics.</p><p>It's <strong>fungus.</strong> And nothing you've tried was made to reach it.</p><p>Most products sit on the surface... or suppress. But almost nothing penetrates.</p>"
        },
        {
          "type": "image_picker",
          "id": "image",
          "label": "Image"
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
  "presets": [
    {
      "name": "KC Problem / Solution",
      "blocks": [
        {
          "type": "block",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Your Nails Aren't Damaged — They're Infected",
            "text": "<p>Years of exposure to moisture, public spaces, and tight shoes didn't weaken your nails — they <strong>infected</strong> them with fungus that burrowed deep under the surface.</p><p>That yellowing? That thickness? That crumbling? It's not aging. It's not genetics.</p><p>It's <strong>fungus.</strong> And nothing you've tried was made to reach it.</p><p>Most products sit on the surface... or suppress. But almost nothing penetrates.</p>"
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "block",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Most Nail Treatments Mask — They Don't Penetrate.",
            "text": "<p>Most nail fungus treatments underdose the one thing that matters — <strong>penetration through the nail bed.</strong></p><p>Keraclear delivers a high-potency oil-based formula that absorbs directly through the nail plate — not weak creams, not surface polishes.</p><p>It's combined with tea tree oil and undecylenic acid to fight fungus and flush it out.</p><p>Why oil? Because creams sit on top. <strong>This absorbs deep. Reaches the source. Clears you out.</strong></p>"
          }
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}
{% endschema %}
